column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/47cda6a1e52efc9dbc017608bb473c7891f7ee40 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
This is not necessary, as status.ToString() is already printed out in all places that call HandleError in the first place. Closing.\n
